Table C_PIB_DEVICE_RELATION

Card of table C_PIB_DEVICE_RELATION

Name

C_PIB_DEVICE_RELATION


Description of the table C_PIB_DEVICE_RELATION

20-Nov-2022

 

DeviceRelation: Capture and manages relationships between a source device or device component and a target device or device component:

 

1. Source device to target device

2. Source device to target device component

3. Source device component to target device

4. Source device component to target device component

 

 

Example:

 

Embedded Software IntelliVue Monitor with product number: 866060

 

Equipment 70464637 with Hardware Serial No.: DE35165102

Equipment 70480991 with SW Serial No.: 6834-6EAZ-N

 

Source: IBIN.OBJECTTYP= '0003'

 

Update Frequency: Daily delta for CRTIM and UPTIM
